  "prompt": "Which is the best college for mathematics honors: Sri Venkateswara or Hans Raj?",
  "response": "Choosing the best college for Mathematics Honours between Sri Venkateswara College and Hans Raj College depends on several factors, including faculty, infrastructure, placement opportunities, and personal preferences.\n\n1. **Sri Venkateswara College**:\n   - Known for a strong emphasis on academics and research.\n   - Good faculty with expertise in various areas of mathematics.\n   - Active student bodies and organizations that encourage co-curricular activities.\n\n2. **Hans Raj College**:\n   - One of the most prestigious colleges in Delhi University, known for overall excellence.\n   - Offers excellent faculty and support for students pursuing mathematics.\n   - Strong placement cell and a good network for internships and jobs.\n\nBoth colleges have their own strengths. It's advisable to consider your career goals, the campus environment you prefer, and any specific programs or opportunities that either college offers. Visiting the campuses if possible, and talking to current students can also help make a more informed decision.",
